## Third-Party Assets

This repository does NOT include any third-party 3D models, animations,
textures, audio, or other media assets.

The MOD framework provided by this project allows users to inject external
assets (GLB, animations, textures, etc.) locally. Users are solely responsible
for verifying the license of any external assets they use as MODs and for
complying with the terms of those licenses. This project makes no claim over
and accepts no responsibility for any external assets used with the MOD system.
